name: Sleeping beauty
description:
From the collection "inside: Dark side"

if I were the sun, I would always set
No one can see all this suffering from above
And do not set
From the collection "inside: Dark sides" 

And if I were the moon, I would let the earth always be dark
So dark that human beings can always stay asleep
Deep and unfinished sleep
Like a sleeping beauty
Sleeping man is more beautiful
